Package pl.polsl.matrixcalculatorweb.model

Class Matrix<T extends Number>

java.lang.Object
pl.polsl.matrixcalculatorweb.model.Matrix<T>
Type Parameters:
T - generic type which represents the type of matrix's elements extending Number class
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, IMatrix<T>
@Entity public class Matrix<T extends Number> extends Object implements IMatrix<T>, Serializable
A class in the 'model' package. The class implements IMatrix interface and Serializable interface and represents a matrix of any number type. It is also Entity class which is stored inside of a database.
